title: Veeam Managed Servers
agents: veeam_rest
catalog: app/veeam
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors Veeam managed server status via the REST API.

 Managed servers include:
 - VMware vCenter and ESXi hosts
 - Microsoft Hyper-V hosts and clusters
 - System Center VMM
 - Windows and Linux hosts
 - SMB file servers

 The check returns:
 - OK: Server is available
 - WARN: Server is in maintenance mode or has warnings
 - CRIT: Server is unavailable, inaccessible, or offline
 - UNKNOWN: No data or server not found

item:
 The server name

discovery:
 One service is created for each managed server.
